tore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":109,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjL7orrt-uTAxV8aEIHHcliCUdIgYOO5b6ZuJMGygEEGsmWmg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbm5EZW0wemZjQmhEQ29BUU40UVNPLTl1SjFiZ3xBQ3Jtc0tuUm5JaVlyRDNoWDh0YTNydDFvTk9ETlRQNlhxVElFbFhaa0lKNFJXeWZZRjVWcU5aVW9vNXpfRFRlemZsVnB4YWxjY2xieVVsdUVuV19zVjJhQV9rbGN0YjF4ZjlmVFlVZHJEaVZBc2J3MUhuMG9EUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Bibgy-yjgYE","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbm5EZW0wemZjQmhEQ29BUU40UVNPLTl1SjFiZ3xBQ3Jtc0tuUm5JaVlyRDNoWDh0YTNydDFvTk9ETlRQNlhxVElFbFhaa0lKNFJXeWZZRjVWcU5aVW9vNXpfRFRlemZsVnB4YWxjY2xieVVsdUVuV19zVjJhQV9rbGN0YjF4ZjlmVFlVZHJEaVZBc2J3MUhuMG9EUQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=Bibgy-yjgYE","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":221,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBQQ040EGAYiEwjL7orrt-uTAxV8aEIHHcliCUdIgYOO5b6ZuJMGygEEGsmWmg==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbFh5QWpVeXZhV3FYcTFxVUo5dXJsZEJFQzNxd3xBQ3Jtc0trMGdwc1dab3hfUTd1X1VLcEJtclZMbmVkbGgtcmF5R1RrcUlIQ094N0Q2VmhqTWVjQVRyQ2xhdGc2cDE1b2NLclJnLW9fbTY4UUN4MnJwM2JZSklua082Q1N0UHR3Y1E1QThBQVgyNHdoR3pNU0RYRQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26hosted_button_id%3D64QMBRBXQSV6G\u0026v=Bibgy-yjgYE","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"h